The paper discusses the integration of blockchain and database technologies to create a new database application platform. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases). The paper also discusses the security features of the system, which suggests it may also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The system is distributed and has audibility features, which could place it in cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also mentions the data structure of the system, which could place it in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper discusses the practical implementation of the system, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering).
